<%= include part_head %>
	<div class="row col-md-8 col-md-offset-2"  style="padding-left:10px; padding-right:10px;">
		<div class="card">
			<% if(photos.length>1) {%>
				<div id="slides">

					<a href="#" class="slidesjs-previous slidesjs-navigation"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span></a>
					
						<% photos.forEach(function(image) { %>
							<img  src="/img/<%= image %>">
						<% }); %>

					<a href="#" class="slidesjs-next slidesjs-navigation"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a>
				</div>
			<% } %>
			<% if(photos.length==1){ %>
				<div class="col-lg-12 col-sm-12">
					<img style="width:100%;margin-top:20px;" src="/img/<%= photos[0] %>">
				</div>
			<% } %>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
		<div class=" col-md-3 ">
			<div class="card to-show">
				<% photos.forEach(function(image) { %>
					<div style="position:relative;">
						<img class="to-show-img" src="/img/<%= image %>">
						<span class="to-show-desc" style="position:absolute;bottom:3px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.7);width:100%;color:white;overflow:hidden;padding:3px;"><%= image %></span>
					</div>
				<% }); %>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-9 ">
			<div class="card">
				<h1>Hurst Carpentry LLC.</h1>
				<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Phasellus quis arcu aliquam, luctus metus vel, vestibulum augue. Sed vitae fermentum nisi. Cras augue mauris, pretium vitae sapien id, ornare rutrum sem. Maecenas molestie massa lacus, at mollis sapien auctor sed. Donec a vehicula ligula, in tristique risus. Suspendisse pulvinar arcu id ligula sollicitudin rhoncus. Etiam ut mauris sed nisl laoreet semper eget ac lacus. Etiam at egestas nisi. Sed ornare sodales nulla et volutpat. Phasellus nec pellentesque lacus, a placerat dolor. Quisque porta, quam non cursus euismod, turpis libero rutrum orci, nec dictum ligula ligula sed ipsum. Curabitur congue faucibus.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
				<h1>Free Estimate</h1>
				<form class="basic-grey" action="make_estimate" method="post" accept-charset="utf-8">
					<div class="col-md-5">
						<input type="email" name="email" value="" placeholder="Email Address">
						<input type="text" name="type" placeholder="Type of work">
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-5">
						<input type="text" name="name" value="" placeholder="Name">
						<input type="text" name="location" value="" placeholder="Location">
					</div>
					<div class="col-md-12">
						<textarea id="textarea"></textarea>
					</div>
					<input id="shadow" type="text" name="description" style="display:none;" placeholder="Description">
					<div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-8">
						<button type="submit">Submit</button>
					</div>
					<div class="clearfix">
						
					</div>
				</form>
			</div>
			<div class="card">
